formulas.name: gp_mort_male
formulas.formula: look_up(data = life_table, age = current_age, sex = "male", value = "prob_death", bin = T)

formulas.name: gp_mort_female
formulas.formula: look_up(data = life_table, age = current_age, sex = "female", value = "prob_death", bin = T)

formulas.name: target_hr
formulas.description: Hazard ratio of relapse, targeted therapy vs. chemotherapy

formulas.name: immun_hr
formulas.description: Hazard ratio of relapse, immunotherapy vs. chemotherapy

formulas.name: rfs_prob
formulas.formula: define_survival("weibull", shape = rfs_p1, scale = rfs_p2) %>% apply_hr(rfs_hr) %>% compute_surv(state_time, cycle_length_months)

formulas.name: rel_mort
formulas.formula: define_survival("weibull", shape = prs_p1, scale = prs_p2) %>% compute_surv(state_time, cycle_length_months) %>% combine_probs(gp_mort_per_cycle)
